                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-col">
                <h4>Ürünler</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/urunler/bioklimatik-pergola">Bioklimatik Pergola</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/urunler/rolling-roof">Rolling Roof</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/urunler/pergola-sistemleri">Pergola Sistemleri</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/urunler/tente-sistemleri">Tente Sistemleri</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-col">
                <h4>Kurumsal</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/kurumsal/hakkimizda">Hakkımızda</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/iletisim">İletişim</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/kalite-politikamiz">Kalite Politikamız</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-col">
                <h4>İletişim</h4>
                <address>
                    Manavkuyu Mah. Sakarya Cd. No:XX<br>
                    Bayraklı, İzmir, Türkiye<br>
                    <strong><a href="tel:+905xxxxxxxxx">05XX XXX XX XX</a></strong><br>
                    <strong><a href="mailto:info@izmirtentemarket.com">info@izmirtentemarket.com</a></strong>
                </address>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <div class="container bottom-container">
                <p>&copy; {year} İTM Architecture. Tüm Hakları Saklıdır.</p>
                <nav>
                    <a href="/sitemap">Site Haritası</a>
                    <span>|</span>
                    <a href="/impressum">Künye</a>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    .site-footer { 
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        color: #000000ff;
        padding-top: 5rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .footer-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 3rem;
        padding-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    .footer-logo { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .footer-logo img { height: 140px; width: auto; }
    .footer-motto { line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .social-links { display: flex; gap: 1rem; }
    .social-links a { 
        color: #000000ff; 
        transition: color 0.2s ease;
        display: inline-block;
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
    }
    .social-links a:hover { color: white; }
    .footer-col h4 {
        color: black;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        position: relative;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .footer-col h4::after {
        color: black;
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 30px;
        height: 2px;
        background-color: var(--accent-color);
    }
    .footer-col ul { list-style: color: #040404ff; none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
    .footer-col ul li { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .footer-col a { color: #040404ff; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s ease; }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: primary-blue);; }
    .footer-col address { font-style: normal; line-height: 1.8; }
    .footer-col address strong { font-weight: 500; }
    .footer-col address a {
        color: black; /* Telefon ve mail daha belirgin olsun */
    }

    .footer-bottom { border-top: 1px solid #333; padding: 1.5rem 0; }
    .bottom-container { 
        display: flex; 
        flex-direction: column; 
        align-items: center; 
        gap: 1rem; 
        text-align: center;
    }
    .bottom-container nav { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; }
    
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .bottom-container { flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; }
    }
    @media (min-width: 992px) {
        .footer-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1.5fr; /* Sütun genişliklerini özelleştir */
        }
    }
</style>

